[The article does not indicate if these sites are under quarantine until
depopulation or if they are under quarantine until tracing is completed. It
is to be hoped that someone in Canada will provide us with information on
the length/purpose of the quarantine. - Mod.TG

The province of Saskatchewan can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail
